Get the example BED file or BEDset with metadata

bb_example.Rd

Get the example BED file or BEDset with metadata

bb_example(api, rec_type = c("bed", "bedset"))

Arguments

api

API object of BEDbase created from BEDbase()

rec_type

character() bed or bedset

Value

list() bed or bedset

Examples

api <- BEDbase()
#> Warning: incomplete final line found on '/tmp/RtmpJmN7Sc/file91b39ccbc8'
bb_example(api, "bed")
